===Etymology===
From [[Greek]] [[νεολιθικός]] (''neolithikos''), from [[Ancient Greek]] prefix [[νεο-]] 
"[[neo-]]", from [[νέος]] (''neos'') "new, young" + [[λίθος]] (''lithos'') "stone".

===Adjective===
'''Neolithic''' (''no [[comparative]] or [[superlative]]'')

# Of or relating to the [[New Stone Age]].

